Title: I Like to Watch
Plot: The CSIs become the focus of a reality TV series, which follows them while they investigate a serial rapist, who recently gained access to a woman's apartment by posing as a fireman.  Also, Warrick's work on the late-shift is causing problems with his marriage to Tina.
GuestStars: Louise Lombard, Wallace Langham, Taraji P. Henson, Liz Vassey, Jack Noseworthy, Karis Campbell, Brett Rickaby, Archie Kao, Anna Van Hooft, Larry Sullivan, Graham Beckel
